---
// Hikvision Landing Page with Poppins Font
---

<head>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#f1f7ff] to-[#e6f0ff] py-16 relative overflow-hidden" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Text content -->
            <div class="md:w-1/2 animate-fade-in-left">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#32869f] to-[#4fb3d9] bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6 leading-tight animate-bounce-in" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
                    Empowering Smart Cities with Cutting-Edge Security Solutions.
                </h1>
                
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-md leading-relaxed mb-8 animate-fade-in text-justify" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
                    Welcome to <strong>Hikvision Dubai</strong>, your one-stop partner for cutting-edge surveillance solutions. We deal in <strong>Hikvision CCTV camera, Hikvision IP camera, and Hikvision ColorVu technology</strong> to provide security solutions for homes, businesses, and industries.
                    Our Hikvision camera solutions, such as Hikvision WiFi camera models, provide hassle-free connectivity and remote viewing. Built for reliability and high-quality imaging, our products incorporate <strong>DarkFighter technology, TandemVu technology, and AcuSense technology</strong> to cater to varied security requirements.
                    At Hikvision Dubai, we provide affordable<strong> Hikvision camera price </strong>without sacrificing quality. Whatever you require to have high-definition video surveillance, night vision, or integrate smart AI, we have the ideal solution.					
                </p>    
                <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#32869f] to-[#4fb3d9] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-opacity-90 group" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
                    <span class="text-sm">Discover More</span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Video section -->
            <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full animate-fade-in-right">
                <div class="relative aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                    <!-- Video thumbnail -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/building.jpg');">
                        <!-- Fallback image in case background doesn't load -->
                        <img src="/building.jpg" alt="Keltron Building" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0" />
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Play button -->
                    <button class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center transition-all hover:bg-blue-700">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" />
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    
                    <!-- Video controls bar -->
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent text-white flex items-center p-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
                        <button class="mr-3 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" />
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <span class="text-sm mr-3 font-medium">0:00 / 0:47</span>
                        
                        <div class="flex-grow mx-3 bg-white/30 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="bg-blue-500 h-full w-0 rounded-full"></div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.536 8.464a5 5 0 010 7.072m2.828-9.9a9 9 0 010 12.728M5.586 15.536a5 5 0 01-1.414-7.072m-2.829 9.9a9 9 0 010-12.728" />
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-lisjoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 8V4m0 0h4M4 4l5 5m11-1V4m0 0h-4m4 0l-5 5M4 16v4m0 0h4m-4 0l5-5m11 5v-4m0 4h-4m4 0l-5-5" />
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                            <button class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 5v.01M12 12v.01M12 19v.01M12 6a1 1 0 110-2 1 1 0 010 2zm0 7a1 1 0 110-2 1 1 0 010 2zm0 7a1 1 0 110-2 1 1 0 010 2z" />
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% { opacity: 0; }
        100% { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInLeft {
        0% { 
            opacity: 0; 
            transform: translateX(-30px);
        }
        100% { 
            opacity: 1; 
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInRight {
        0% { 
            opacity: 0; 
            transform: translateX(30px);
        }
        100% { 
            opacity: 1; 
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes bounceIn {
        0% { 
            opacity: 0; 
            transform: scale(0.7);
        }
        50% { 
            opacity: 1; 
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }
        70% { 
            transform: scale(0.97);
        }
        100% { 
            transform: scale(1);
        }
    }

    .animate-fade-in {
        animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-fade-in-left {
        animation: fadeInLeft 1.2s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-fade-in-right {
        animation: fadeInRight 1.2s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-bounce-in {
        animation: bounceIn 1.2s ease-out;
    }
</style>